/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a sense of motion and journey. The sky above is a clear blue, providing a vibrant backdrop to the scene. On either side of the road, lush green trees stand tall, their leaves rustling in the breeze. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. Power lines crisscross above, forming a complex web against the sky. The image is taken from a low angle, which emphasizes the height of the trees and buildings, making them appear grand and imposing. The colors in the image are bright and vibrant, with the green of the trees contrasting beautifully with the blue sky.
